<% title= "Fitness for Women | Women's Health Hub"  %>


<div class="container py-5">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-8">
      <h1 class="mb-4">Fitness & Exercise for Women</h1>
      <p class="lead mb-4">Regular physical activity is one of the most important things you can do for your health. Discover exercise options tailored to women's unique needs across different life stages.</p>
      
      <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">Benefits of Regular Exercise</h5>
          
          <div class="row mb-4">
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 me-3">
                  <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="width: 50px; height: 50px;">
                    <i class="fas fa-heart fa-lg"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h6>Heart Health</h6>
                  <p class="mb-0">Reduces risk of heart disease and improves cardiovascular function. Particularly important for women, as heart disease is the leading cause of death among women.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 me-3">
                  <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="width: 50px; height: 50px;">
                    <i class="fas fa-bone fa-lg"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h6>Bone Strength</h6>
                  <p class="mb-0">Weight-bearing exercise helps maintain bone density, reducing risk of osteoporosis, which disproportionately affects women after menopause.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="row mb-4">
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 me-3">
                  <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="width: 50px; height: 50px;">
                    <i class="fas fa-brain fa-lg"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h6>Mental Wellbeing</h6>
                  <p class="mb-0">Reduces symptoms of anxiety and depression, improves mood, and enhances cognitive function. Women experience higher rates of certain mood disorders.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 me-3">
                  <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="width: 50px; height: 50px;">
                    <i class="fas fa-apple-alt fa-lg"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h6>Metabolic Health</h6>
                  <p class="mb-0">Improves insulin sensitivity, helps maintain healthy weight, and reduces risk of type 2 diabetes, which affects women's hormonal health.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="row mb-4">
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 me-3">
                  <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="width: 50px; height: 50px;">
                    <i class="fas fa-female fa-lg"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h6>Hormonal Balance</h6>
                  <p class="mb-0">Can help regulate menstrual cycles, manage PCOS symptoms, and reduce severity of menopausal symptoms like hot flashes.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 me-3">
                  <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="width: 50px; height: 50px;">
                    <i class="fas fa-moon fa-lg"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h6>Better Sleep</h6>
                  <p class="mb-0">Improves sleep quality and duration, which is crucial for hormonal health, cognitive function, and stress management.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="alert alert-info">
            <i class="fas fa-lightbulb me-2"></i> <strong>Did you know?</strong> The US Department of Health and Human Services recommends at least 150 minutes of moderate-intensity aerobic activity or 75 minutes of vigorous-intensity activity per week, plus muscle-strengthening activities at least twice per week.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">Types of Exercise</h5>
          
