                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><strong>Perimenopause</strong></td>
                  <td>Addressing hormonal fluctuations and changing body composition</td>
                  <td>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                      <li>Increased strength training to maintain muscle mass</li>
